song_name: From The Ritz To The Rubble
lyrics:

well last night these two bouncers
and one of ems alright the other ones a scaryun

how he dont want you to so step out the queue

its just something to talk about a story to tell yeah

chorus
well im so glad they turned us all away well put it down to fate
